<li id="cite_note-WilsonClinton-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-WilsonClinton_20-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.hillaryclinton.com/news/release/view/?id=2426" class="external text" title="http://www.hillaryclinton.com/news/release/view/?id=2426" rel="nofollow">"Frm. Ambassador Joseph Wilson Endorses Clinton"</a>, press release, online posting, <i><a href="/wiki/Hillary_Clinton" title="Hillary Clinton" class="mw-redirect">Hillary Clinton.com</a></i> (official site), July 16, 2007, accessed July 23, 2007.</li>
