gory:United_States_ambassadors_to_Gabon" title="Category:United States ambassadors to Gabon">United States ambassadors to Gabon</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:United_States_ambassadors_to_S%C3%A3o_Tom%C3%A9_and_Pr%C3%ADncipe" title="Category:United States ambassadors to São Tomé and Príncipe">United States ambassadors to São Tomé and Príncipe</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:1949_births" title="Category:1949 births">1949 births</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Living_people" title="Category:Living people">Living people</a></span></div><div id="mw-hidden-catlinks" class="mw-hidden-cats-hidden">Hidden categories:&#32;<span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:All_pages_needing_cleanup" title="Category:All pages needing cleanup">All pages needing cleanup</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Wikipedia_articles_needing_clarification_from_August_2008" title="Category:Wikipedia articles needing clarification from August 2008">Wikipedia articles needing clarification from August 2008</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:NPOV_disputes_from_August_2008" title="Category:NPOV disputes from August 2008">NPOV disputes from August 2008</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Accuracy_disputes_from_August_2008" title="Category:Accuracy disputes from August 2008">Accuracy disputes from August 2008</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:All_NPOV_disputes" title="Category:All NPOV disputes">All NPOV disputes</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:All_articles_with_unsourced_statements" title="Category:All articles with unsourced statements">All articles with unsourced statements</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Articles_with_unsourced_statements_since_January_2008" title="Category:Articles with unsourced statements since January 2008">Articles with unsourced statements since January 2008</a></span></div></div>			<!-- end content -->
